Dear Maintainers,

Please keep in mind that we are on schedule for our release as given in
http://bioconductor.org/developers/release-schedule/

Today (Nov 1st 2022) at 9:00 am ET, We will freeze the commits to all the branches and all packages in Bioconductor. We will notify here once we are done with the Release process.

Once again, After 9:00 am today, you will temporarily not be able to push to the bioconductor git repo.

Cheers,




